name: Parasite Infected Panda - KuD-047
description: Do you know about Orinoid meteor shower ? yeah its coming around halloween, whats more about that is this one bring unknown entity to pandas planet. This panda is one of dead panda being controlled by them, he was dead by car accident and now his body roaming the streets because of this worm who search for more brains to eat. Halloween becoming more and more scary because of them.
